{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"VGLSQgjkL1invoOn1WIVU","title":"Operation Rewrite","desc":"","updated":1645083833005,"created":1644384514239,"custom":{},"fname":"projects.operation-rewrite","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"fe9f7a41500e3da0648b38257c274730","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"projects.operation-rewrite","id":"VGLSQgjkL1invoOn1WIVU","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"web.frontend.designpatterns","alias":"web.frontend.designpatterns","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":5,"offset":660},"end":{"line":28,"column":36,"offset":691},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"web.frontend.designpatterns"}}],"anchors":{"project-operation-re-write-purposely-obscure":{"type":"header","text":"Project: Operation Re-write (Purposely obscure)","value":"project-operation-re-write-purposely-obscure","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"problem":{"type":"header","text":"Problem:","value":"problem","line":10,"column":0,"depth":3},"solution":{"type":"header","text":"Solution:","value":"solution","line":14,"column":0,"depth":3},"existing-stack":{"type":"header","text":"Existing stack","value":"existing-stack","line":18,"column":0,"depth":3},"proposed-re-architected-stack":{"type":"header","text":"Proposed re-architected stack:","value":"proposed-re-architected-stack","line":25,"column":0,"depth":3},"rendering-style":{"type":"header","text":"Rendering Style","value":"rendering-style","line":32,"column":0,"depth":3},"framework-options":{"type":"header","text":"Framework Options","value":"framework-options","line":42,"column":0,"depth":3},"headless-cms-options":{"type":"header","text":"Headless CMS Options","value":"headless-cms-options","line":48,"column":0,"depth":3},"db":{"type":"header","text":"DB?","value":"db","line":53,"column":0,"depth":3}},"children":[],"parent":"6FtP5bCaxDDd47jEuSH5y","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"operation-rewrite\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#operation-rewrite\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Operation Rewrite</h1>\n<h2 id=\"project-operation-re-write-purposely-obscure\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#project-operation-re-write-purposely-obscure\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Project: Operation Re-write (Purposely obscure)</h2>\n<h3 id=\"problem\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#problem\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Problem:</h3>\n<p>Existing site is slow and difficult to improve given it's built in wordpress. Gives limited options for improvement from a developer perspective without adding more bloat and plugins. Owned by non-for-profit therefore budget is an important consideration.</p>\n<h3 id=\"solution\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#solution\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Solution:</h3>\n<p>Re-write using headless CMS and following JAMSTACK princples.</p>\n<h3 id=\"existing-stack\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#existing-stack\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Existing stack</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Frontend: PHP</li>\n<li>Backend: PHP</li>\n<li>CMS: Wordpress</li>\n<li>DB: SQL</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"proposed-re-architected-stack\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#proposed-re-architected-stack\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Proposed re-architected stack:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Frontend: React framework</li>\n<li>Backend - possibly NodeJS with GraphQL</li>\n<li>CMS: Headless</li>\n<li>DB: ?? not sure if I need one</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"rendering-style\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#rendering-style\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Rendering Style</h3>\n<p>Ref <a href=\"/KnowledgeGarden/notes/KnACyiSV918ASnIeSH2TQ\">Rendering Design Patterns</a></p>\n<p>Options: SSR, SSG, SPA, ISR</p>\n<p>Content is mostly static - new blog posts written relatively infrequently. There is an ecommerce section with a small number of products. No comments or anything else that is dynamic at the moment.</p>\n<p>SSG could be a good option here but a framework that supports SSR as well could be useful for any future concerns. Maybe best of both worlds and use ISR? No need to rebuild every time we change a post or add a product.</p>\n<h3 id=\"framework-options\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#framework-options\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Framework Options</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Remix - looks good but pretty new</li>\n<li>Next - established, but maybe bloated for my use case? Needs a server to run for ISR and SSR</li>\n<li>Gatsby - only does SSG (?)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"headless-cms-options\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#headless-cms-options\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Headless CMS Options</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Strapi - free/open source</li>\n<li>Contentful - recommended but paid after certain point</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"db\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#db\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>DB?</h3>\n<p>Do I need?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>PSQL</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"wn8PE1RhG0znK1alrGFYv","title":"Knowledge Garden","desc":"","updated":1644116275124,"created":1631901573363,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"ae1897c5e907720acd7db1adf9dfd832","links":[],"anchors":{"my-second-brain":{"type":"header","text":"My Second B